name: HUMANATURE (2020)
description: By @sashastiles, minted as a #CleanNFT on #EarthDay2021. A reminder that however quickly we humans evolve, we are never separate from the earth and its other inhabitants — we are irrevocably interconnected with nature. Originally curated by Judy Chicago for #CreateArtforEarth and exhibited in “Solstice: Create Art for Earth” at Turner Carroll Gallery, Santa Fe, June-July 2020. Sasha Stiles is a Pushcart-nominated poet and artist working at the intersection of text and technology. sashastiles.com
